title: It would be funny, kind of, if AI advisors with humanity's collective wisdom caused a collapse in cognitive diversity.
pid: e69bd4e2-1477-48e4-a8f0-ab3846908e7a
body: |2-
  You could also argue the opposite:
  That giving people solutions to known problems
  frees up their time that
  would have cognitively overlapped others' work,
  permitting greater cognitive diversity.
